{"tid":1876788,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"咒《環時》、中共染肺炎，與胡錫進對罵，大鱷巴斯：你們是人類恥辱","createTime":"2020-02-12T15:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T15:56:31.000Z","uid":104138,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dce6b1656e8bffe0d667377830d56f0f6d9ccf75","tid":1876788,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:31:05.000Z","msg":"美國國國務卿蓬佩奧早前在Twitter上的一則帖文，觸發近年常唱淡港元及中國經濟的知名對沖基金大鱷巴斯（Kyle Bass）與內地官媒《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進互相對罵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://businessfocus.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/24550608-7986727-image-a-12_1581335839070.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F24550608-7986727-image-a-12_1581335839070.jpg&h=44f6e330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事緣胡錫進於上周六在蓬佩奧的Twitter帖文留言，認為美國對華疫情的支援實在來得太遲，此舉引起巴斯不滿，他更「爆粗」留言，反指美國應該放棄協助中國遏制疫情，甚至取回所有物資，「讓病毒橫掃《環球時報》和中國共產黨。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://businessfocus.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/ntow2OuOkMZhTeYCE15xUcnKNzi2G6_UkJ_0T5Cf9E8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2Fntow2OuOkMZhTeYCE15xUcnKNzi2G6_UkJ_0T5Cf9E8.jpg&h=38946b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然事後巴斯刪除該帖文，但胡錫進再發文指責對方發出如此詛咒，要求道歉。結果巴斯發帖文，拒絕道歉，更反諷中方處理疫情手法：「中共譴責、懲罰武漢的英雄。只有上帝才知道其餘7個通報肺炎醫生的遭遇。你們是人類的恥辱。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://businessfocus.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/24549384-7986727-image-m-13_1581336079495.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F24549384-7986727-image-m-13_1581336079495.jpg&h=9939fe6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴斯事後在聲明中補充，自己把帖文刪除是因為覺得先前言論對《環球時報》的大部分員工太苛刻，強調他絕不會向自以為是、企圖操縱公眾言論的人道歉。據了解，巴斯是對沖基金海曼資本的創辦人，早前更預測本港今年會爆發全面的銀行業危機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://businessfocus.io/article/129750/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%92%92-%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E6%9F%93%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%88%87%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%E5%B0%8D%E7%BD%B5-%E5%A4%A7%E9%B1%B7%E5%B7%B4%E6%96%AF-%E4%BD%A0%E5%80%91%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%A1%9E%E6%81%A5%E8%BE%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.io%2Farticle%2F129750%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2592%2592-%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E6%259F%2593%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%2583%25A1%25E9%258C%25AB%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25BD%25B5-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25B1%25B7%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%2596%25AF-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%2580%2591%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25A1%259E%25E6%2581%25A5%25E8%25BE%25B1&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GCJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=d61c5f19\" target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.io/article/129750/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%92%92-%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E6%9F%93%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%88%87%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%E5%B0%8D%E7%BD%B5-%E5%A4%A7%E9%B1%B7%E5%B7%B4%E6%96%AF-%E4%BD%A0%E5%80%91%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%A1%9E%E6%81%A5%E8%BE%B1</a>"},{"pid":"fd047455196870fbf823e39d93ff5e102fefecbc","tid":1876788,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:33:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ffd341cb4613f365e6537e227edd9cb170511cf1","tid":1876788,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:48:22.000Z","msg":"又係共匪話自己可防可控，環時就癲狗上身話美國幫得遲?<br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句，幫你班蝗係人情，唔幫係道理"},{"pid":"2b4d647fe21180c44b2ac5c3f1fd5067948dc4dd","tid":1876788,"uid":169074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:50:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc90364796594382060a84f40ecfa3b38061d26c","tid":1876788,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"「早前更預測本港今年會爆發全面的銀行業危機」<br />\n大家小心啦"},{"pid":"abe81f0acafbe8781eeee4d0f8a2342343a994d5","tid":1876788,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:56:31.000Z","ms